The paper deals with image matching, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed benchmark and evaluation metrics are designed to assess the overall performance of image matching methods, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The authors also compare and analyze different state-of-the-art methods, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
